item.title: NEM Clouds 28 - The James Clarke Selection
item.description:
NEM Clouds 28 - The James Clarke Selection

Round #28 - Things are heating up in Cloud-land. We're getting some real competition & selecting 8 images was pretty tough this time (which definitely beats the alternative). Congratulations to all selected and as always, please invite all your Cloudy friends to join and participate!
